content: In CSV format, compile a list of ten favorite snacks from around the world, along with their country of origin and main ingredients.

Sure! Here's a list of ten favorite snacks from around the world in CSV format, including their country of origin and main ingredients:

"Snack Name","Country of Origin","Main Ingredients"
"Chips","United States","Potatoes, vegetable oil, salt"
"Wasabi Peas","Japan","Green peas, wasabi powder, soy sauce, sugar"
"Chocolat","Switzerland","Cocoa solids, sugar, cocoa butter"
"Cheese Balls","Global","Cheese, breadcrumbs, spices"
"Korean Fried Chicken","South Korea","Chicken, flour, eggs, breadcrumbs, soy sauce, sugar, pepper, sesame seeds"
"French Fries","Belgium","Potatoes, vegetable oil, salt"
"Nachos","Mexico","Tortilla chips, cheese, salsa, guacamole, sour cream"
"Popcorn","United States","Corn, vegetable oil, salt"
"Jelly Beans","United States","Sugar, corn syrup, starch, pectin, food coloring, flavoring"
"Truffles","France","Chocolate, cream, sometimes with inclusions like nuts or fruit"
